item.title: 309 Crime Adjacent, with Lindsay Sharman
item.description: <strong>We're back on our Patreon live zoom for this episode, and joining in the fun and frolics is writer and podcaster, Lindsay Sharman, whose own life of crime displays more of a wrong place at the wrong time vibe than clear intent, but has landed her in just as much hot water, so it's no surprise that the bad company she keeps means she has a keen eye for getting to the root of criminal behaviour... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/580adc7a-3ec4-4ee1-a811-02ba70ad9aad
